<HEAD>Carmen <HI>Steliteutieon.</HI></HEAD>
<L>EUGE SY GERYONOS RHOPALO TRIA SOMATA RIPSAS,</L>
<L>AMPHITRIONIADES HOS MEGAS ALLOS ESE,</L>
<L>HEIMATI T'ALLOTRIO SEO CERBERE KEUTHE KARENON.</L>
<L>OU DYNATON PHOREEIN EELIOIO PHAOS.</L>
