<P>As the Devil is originally the Author of <HI>Charms,</HI> and <HI>Spells,</HI> so is he the Author of several baudy Songs, which are sung. A re|verend Minister told me, that one who was the Devils Piper, a wizzard confest to him, that at a Ball of dancing, the Foul Spirit taught him a Baudy song to sing and play, as it were this night, and ere two days past all the Lads and Lasses of the town were lilting it throw the street. It were abomination to rehearse it.</P>
